== 製作 ==
有別於首集的[[美國自然歷史博物館|美國自然歷史博物館]]，本片場景轉移至位於美國首府[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]][[史密森尼博物館|史密森尼博物館]]，是全球最大的博物館群兼研究中心，主要在旗下的[[美国国立自然历史博物馆|美国国立自然历史博物馆]]拍摄。史密森尼研究中心首次開放電影實景拍攝，不過必須在開放時間進行，因此拍攝過程中，得面對許多遊客現場圍觀。<ref>{{cite web | title = 全世界第一大博物館稀奇風光《博物館驚魂夜2》首度揭曉 | publisher = 奇摩電影 | url = http://tw.movie.yahoo.com/movieheadline/d/a/090504/3/f1b.html | accessdate = 2009-05-11 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090509024823/http://tw.movie.yahoo.com/movieheadline/d/a/090504/3/f1b.html | archivedate = 2009-05-09 }}</ref>

此外，考量動作打鬥追逐戲不適合于館內拍攝，許多場景另外搭景而成，如博物館大廳、國家航空與太空博物館、史密森尼總部城堡和[[林肯紀念堂|林肯紀念堂]]，以及館內的[[火箭|火箭]]、[[太空船|阿波羅太空船]]和[[萊特兄弟|萊特兄弟]]的[[古董|古董]][[飛機|飛機]]皆重新仿製。

== 評價 ==
該片得到影評混合平均評語。電影評論網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]，基於119篇評論中43％給予正面的評價，平均得分為5.1/10。爛番茄網站裡的「頂尖影評」統計，包含來自報章雜誌、廣播電視與網路的知名影評，基於當中27篇評論，影片整體得到33%的正面評價。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/night_at_the_museum_2_escape_from_the_smithsonian/?critic=creamcrop | title=Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian Movie Reviews, Pictures - Cream of the Crop | work=Rotten Tomatoes | publisher=IGN Entertianment | accessdate=2009-05-22 | archive-date=2020-09-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922190341/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/night_at_the_museum_2_escape_from_the_smithsonian?critic=creamcrop | dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]其中一個標準化評價滿分為100的影評，根據27篇總和，電影平均分數獲得44分。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/nightatthemuseum2?q=Night%20at%20the%20Museum:%20Battle%20of%20the%20Smithsonian | title=Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian (2009): Reviews | publisher=Metacritic | accessdate=2009-05-22 | archive-date=2009-08-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090821141947/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/nightatthemuseum2?q=Night%20at%20the%20Museum%3A%20Battle%20of%20the%20Smithsonian | dead-url=no }}</ref>

儘管混合評語來自各方影評，大多數評論家稱讚[[艾美·亞當斯|艾美·亞當斯]]和[[漢克·阿扎里亞|漢克·阿扎里亞]]的表演。《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的麥可菲利浦授予電影3顆星指出，“……她實為驚人——銀光幕上亮眼演出。”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/chi-tc-mov-night-museum-0520-052may20,0,6390332.story | title=Toys in the nation's attic - Amy Adams a treasure in the 'Museum' sequel | publisher=Chicago Tribune | accessdate=2009-05-22 | date=2009-05-20 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090527030719/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/movies/chi-tc-mov-night-museum-0520-052may20%2C0%2C6390332.story | archivedate=2009-05-27 }}</ref>《[[娛樂週刊|娛樂週刊]]》的歐文·吉博曼也給此片「B+」的評分，表示“亞當斯賦予了本片豐富的生命力。”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20279927,00.html | title=Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian - Entertianment Weekly | date=2009-05-19 | accessdate=2009-05-22 | publisher=Entertainment Weekly | archive-date=2009-05-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090529081150/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20279927,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>儘管《電視指南》的佩瑞·塞伯特給電影2顆星，仍表示「感謝阿扎里亞，抓取漫畫時機的大師。收納古怪角色的當他的爪牙是有趣的點，像是芝麻街的奧斯卡和[[達斯·維德|達斯·維德]]加入他的團隊。」<ref>{{cite web | url=http://movies.tvguide.com/night-museum-battle-smithsonian/review/297477 | title=Night At The Museum: Battle Of The Smithsonian: Review | publisher=TV Guide | accessdate=2009-05-22 | archive-date=2013-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012152152/http://movies.tvguide.com/night-museum-battle-smithsonian/review/297477 | dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》的麥可·瑞奇薛芬和《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的A.O.史考特都喜愛兩位的演出。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film-reviews/film-review-night-at-the-museum-battle-of-1003974548.story | title=Film Review: Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian | publisher=Hollywood Reporter | accessdate=2009-05-22 | date=2009-05-20 | archive-date=2009-05-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090525020625/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/film-reviews/film-review-night-at-the-museum-battle-of-1003974548.story | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://movies.nytimes.com/2009/05/22/movies/22nigh.html?ref=movies | title=Movie Review:Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian (2009) - Dad’s at Another Museum. Does That Make Him an Exhibitionist? | date=2009-05-22 | accessdate=2009-05-22 | publisher=New York Times | archive-date=2009-05-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090526090456/http://movies.nytimes.com/2009/05/22/movies/22nigh.html?ref=movies | dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，大多數的電影評論家批評其過度使用的特殊效果，斯科特·托比亞斯於《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》指出，這部電影是“一個令人費解的情節和為特效而特效的擁擠安排。”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/night-at-the-museum-battle-of-the-smithsonian,28233/?utm_source=channel_film | title=Night at the Museum: Battle of the Smithsonian Review - A.V. Club | publisher=A.V. Club | accessdate=2009-05-22 | date=2009-05-21 | archive-date=2012-10-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121006162204/http://www.avclub.com/articles/night-at-the-museum-battle-of-the-smithsonian,28233/?utm_source=channel_film | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 穿帮镜头 ==
=== 不规则的光影 ===
在法老王打开通向冥界的门以后，他的地下士兵鱼贯而出。由于法老王之门内发出巨大的光芒，走出士兵的影子方向是远离门的。而站在与门不远的同一直线上的拉瑞的影子，却是朝向法老王之门，显示出其身后有不该反映在镜头中的光源。

